crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET POLICY TLS possible TOR SSL traffic
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp any ![21,25,110,143,443,465,587,636,989:995,5061,5222,8443] -> any any (msg:"ET POLICY TLS possible TOR SSL traffic"; flow:established,from_server; tls.cert_issuer; content:"CN=www"; startswith; content:".com"; endswith; pcre:"/^CN=www\.[0-9a-z]{8,20}\.com$/"; tls.cert_subject; content:"CN=www"; startswith; content:".net"; endswith; pcre:"/^CN=www\.[0-9a-z]{8,20}\.net$/"; classtype:misc-activity; sid:2018789; rev:4; metadata:created_at 2014_07_28, former_category POLICY, updated_at 2021_07_23;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: SURICATA HTTP Request abnormal Content-Encoding header
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http any any -> any any (msg:"SURICATA HTTP Request abnormal Content-Encoding header"; flow:established,to_server; app-layer-event:http.abnormal_ce_header; flowint:http.anomaly.count,+,1; classtype:protocol-command-decode; sid:2221033; rev:1;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET P2P Tor Get Server Request
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert http $HOME_NET any -> $EXTERNAL_NET any (msg:"ET P2P Tor Get Server Request"; flow:established,to_server; http.uri; content:"/tor/server/"; nocase; reference:url,tor.eff.org; reference:url,doc.emergingthreats.net/2008113; classtype:policy-violation; sid:2008113; rev:5; metadata:created_at 2010_07_30, updated_at 2020_09_01;)

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: ET POLICY TOR Consensus Data Requested

crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_msg: POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt
crowdsourced_ids_results.rule_raw: alert tcp any any -> any $HTTP_PORTS ( msg:"POLICY-OTHER HTTP request by IPv4 address attempt"; flow:to_server,established; http_header; content:"Host:",fast_pattern,nocase; pcre:"/^Host\x3a\s*(?:(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\.){3}(?:25[0-5]|2[0-4][0-9]|[01]?[0-9]?[0-9])\s*:?\s*\d*\s*$/smi"; service:http; reference:url,www.w3.org/Protocols/rfc2616/rfc2616-sec15.html; classtype:policy-violation; sid:50447; rev:1; )
